Marisol Ayuso https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marisol_Ayuso 0 Marisol Ayuso (born May 19, 1943 in Madrid) is a Spanish stage, movie and television actress. Her father, Pedro Pablo Ayuso, was also an actor, and her mother, María Soledad Domínguez Giraldes, was an aristocrat (the granddaughter of the Viscount of Troncoso).She has a daughter with the former director of the General Spanish Society of Authors (SGAE) who was the owner of the disco "Pachá" in the 1980s.
